imdb.plot outline: Do you work in a cubicle? Have you been included on an email chain that just won't die? Embarrass yourself on a conference call? Have to work on the weekend? Dodge the office cold? Deal with the IT Department? Setup your voicemail? Work with an intern? Or become addicted to caffeine? We know how you feel. "the CUBICLE" is a series that relates to the plight of those whose jobs need a bit of comedy. Centered on a guy named Guy, each episode follows the various misadventures he experiences while working in his tiny cubicle.
imdb.title: The Cubicle
